rComments: LOVED THIS COURSE and my mark reflected it. He don't just talk he TEACHES you, and yes his midterms and exams do feature unknowns but he teaches you the skills to identify them and it is the most rewarding feeling ever. Definitely go for it! He's so awesome you'll love it. You won't want to miss a class!

Great lecturer, but expects an unreasonable amount from his students. Tests were incredibly hard (features slide images that are completely UNKNOWN). Learnt a lot, but my GPA suffered. Worst mark I've ever gotten in a UofT art history course.
